set incsearch
map <F7> <ESC>:nohlsearch<CR>
set hlsearch
colorscheme desert

imap <F10> <ESC>:wa<CR>
map <F10> <ESC>:wa<CR>
imap <A-F10> <ESC>:wqa<CR>
